{"comments":"Layer — 3D layer system, rotation order, parenting, and null objects.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nThis module provides the layer-level transform features:\n\n- **LayerDimensionality** — 2D vs 3D layer modes\n- **RotationOrder** — Euler angle order for 3D rotation\n- **LayerParenting** — Parent-child relationships (pick-whip)\n- **LayerTransformState** — Complete layer transform with parenting\n- **NullObject** — Invisible transform-only layers for rigging\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- AnimatedTransform.Transform (AnimatedTransform2D, AnimatedTransform3D)\n- AnimatedTransform.Evaluation (evaluateTransform2DAt, evaluateTransform3DAt)\n- Schema.Dimension.Temporal (Frames)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[107,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/AnimatedTransform/Layer.purs","start":[107,3]},"title":"Layer2D"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[108,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/AnimatedTransform/Layer.purs","start":[108,3]},"title":"Layer3D"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Motion","AnimatedTransform","Layer"],"LayerDimensionality"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[110,64],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/AnimatedTransform/Layer.purs","start":[110,1]},"title":"eqLayerDimensionality"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Motion","AnimatedTransform","Layer"],"LayerDimensionality"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[114,22],"n